                                    Card EMI Txns on a Net Cart Value of ₹40,000
                                    and above{' '}
                                    <span style={{ color: 'blue' }}>
                                        <strong>T&C</strong>
                                    </span>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <LoyaltyIcon
                                        fontSize="small"
